[ ✨GIVEAWAY!!✨ ]

I am staying at home and... BBQ!

With this eco-friendly biodegradable disposal barbecue pit, now you can BBQ anytime anywhere at home!

No fire starter or charcoal needed! Just prepare your food and start to BBQ! Love how it’s lightweight and portable! It just takes less than 3 mins to setup, and it’s able to retain its heat for approx. 60 mins!

I’ll be giving away one set of Disposable BBQ pit to 3 lucky winners each!

To win : 
1️⃣ Follow @gnitiyyiting and @TSDirect
2️⃣ Like this post 
3️⃣ Tag a Friend and comment “I want FREE bbq pit!”
4️⃣ Repost this post on IG stories for bonus entries! (Remember to tag us)

Last entry ends on 10 May 2359! (1 comment = 1 entry)

This giveaway is open to those residing in Singapore only! Good luck!
